00:20:38.923 --> 00:20:42.593
{an8}<i>na talagang bulgar na reynang burles.</i>

276
00:20:48.641 --> 00:20:50.727
<i>Buong araw kong ginawa 'yung eksenang 'yun</i>

277
00:20:50.810 --> 00:20:54.355
