971
01:06:15.282 --> 01:06:18.076
The Lucy
-Desi Comedy Hour!

972
01:06:18.160 --> 01:06:21.538
{an8}<i>Gusto nilang tuloy-tuloy na magtrabaho,</i>
<i>pero magtrabaho nang kaunti,</i>


973
01:06:21.621 --> 01:06:24.124
{an8}<i>kaya sabi nila gagawin nila pareho</i>
<i>ang palabas,</i>


974
01:06:24.207 --> 01:06:26.918
<i>pero gagawin itong buwanan lang.</i>

975
01:06:31.006 --> 01:06:35.886
{an8}<i>Nawalan talaga</i>
